==English==

===Adjective===
# A problem that continues over an extended period of time, often characterized by long suffering.  Prolonged or slow to heal. The opposite of [[acute]]. 
#''(medicine):'' A condition of extended duration, either continuous or marked by frequent recurrence. Sometimes implies a worsening condition (a condition which gets worse with each recurrence).

===Noun===

#''(slang):'' marijuana

